Your Serene Retreat Awaits, nestled in a picturesque neighborhood, this 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem boasts luxurious living spaces and modern amenities that make every day feel like a getaway. The upgraded kitchen is a culinary paradise with sleek upgrades and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. A flowing open floor plan creates an inviting space perfect for entertaining and relaxation. Soaring ceilings add a touch of grandeur to every room as well as the natural light that bathes this home in warmth and beauty. The entire house feature tile flooring for a seamless and elegant look. This home has new roof installed in 2021 and an updated HVAC system in 2020 provide peace of mind and energy efficiency. This home is equipped with a Ring doorbell and Nest thermostat for convenience and security. Savor stunning views from the living room and bedroom balconies, creating the perfect backdrop for every sunrise and sunset. Tranquil, serene, and meticulously designed, this home truly feels like a private retreat. This property combines modern luxury with natural beauty, creating a harmonious oasis you'll cherish. Don't miss the chance to call it your own!
